    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but what if those opt-outs actually harm people though? like if a religious group refuses to follow certain healthcare or equality mandates, isn't that basically just trampling on the rights of others in the name of their \"freedom\"? how do you balance that without the state becoming a mess of exceptions?",
