      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but who actually gets to decide what counts as a \"basic human right\" or \"direct harm\"? it feels like if we let the govt decide whenever they feel like it, they could just label any religious practice they don't like as \"harmful\" to get around the constitution. isn't there a risk that \"protecting public safety\" just becomes an excuse to slowly erase religious influence from public life?",
